We signed on to a letter to MassDOT regarding the “Grounding McGrath” project, spearheaded by [SASS](https://sass-somerville.org), sent to MassDOT leadership on <time datetime="2024-05-14">May 14, 2024</time>.

Please see [“A Letter to Massdot on the Design for the Mcgrath Boulevard Project” on SASS’s website](https://sass-somerville.org/index.php/2024/05/19/a-letter-to-massdot-on-the-design-for-the-mcgrath-boulevard-project/) to read it.
